## 📊 Use Cases

* Read-heavy caching systems
* Database indexing
* Key-value storage engines
* Search systems with range queries

---

## 🔍 Inspiration

This project is inspired by storage systems used in:

* Modern databases (e.g., MySQL InnoDB, PostgreSQL)
* Distributed storage engines
* LSM vs B-Tree design tradeoffs 

